GEDTM30 global 1-arc-second (~30m) Digital Terrain Model (DTM)

Source: R/sources.R
gedtm30_model.Rd

GEDTM30 global 1-arc-second (~30m) Digital Terrain Model (DTM)

gedtm30_model(varname = "legendtm_rf_30m", vsi = TRUE)

Arguments

varname

defaults to 'legendtm_rf_30m' (the elevation)

vsi

include /vsicurl prefix

Value

for 'gedtm30_sources' dataframe of details about the files, for 'gedtm30_model' one of the variables source urls

See also

gedtm30() which returns a single cog url just for the DEM

Examples

gedtm30_model("hillshade_edtm")
